PR
==
(1) Rust:
    cargo clippy -- -D warnings
    cargo fmt
    
(2) Python:
    pyright
    ruff check
    ruff format
    
(3) Tests:
    cargo test
    python3 exa-t.py test
    
(3) Commit msg: concise, clean

(4) PR: clarify whatâ€™s changed and why

(5) Add your name (and optionally your email) to the `AUTHORS` file at project root
